      <h2 id="headline" class="article-full-headline">Kerf</h2>
      <p id="byline" class="article-full-byline">ERICA FUNKHOUSER</p>
      <div>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">What disappears</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">when an eight-foot plank</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">is sawn in half, yielding</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">two less-than-four-foot boards,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">a solid term for what’s lost</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">to the teeth of separation.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">Neither sawdust nor error,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">nor the labor of gremlins</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">waiting to wreak havoc</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">on perfectly accurate</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">measurements.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">Kerf—you will know it</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">by its absence,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">like divided attention.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">Small consolation:</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">each board as it’s halved</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">releases both sides</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">of a single scent,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">limewood for linden,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">pine for pine.</p>
